##Breeding civet cats after the outbreak? Jiangxi Provincial Wild Life Protection Bureau: Not True, related policies to be further defined by the state

Jiangxi Wild Animal Protection Bureau director said, is currently in accordance with the national unified deployment, the province's wild animal breeding industry to map.

Jiangxi Wild Animal Protection Bureau director said, is currently in accordance with the national unified deployment, the province's wild animal breeding industry to map.

”

Recently, an online circular "request will be part of the artificial breeding of wild land animals included in the national management of the request" (hereinafter referred to as "the request") caused concern.

The interface news noted that the request, which was submitted by Jiangxi Province to the Ministry of Agriculture and rural areas and the State Forestry and Grass Bureau, it is requested that some wild animal and bird species with mature and stable artificial breeding techniques, such as civet cats and bamboo rats, be included in the "catalogue of livestock and Poultry Genetic Resources" and be managed in accordance with the provisions of the Animal Husbandry Law and other relevant laws and regulations.

"request for instructions" also pointed out that Jiangxi is a large province of wildlife resources, wildlife artificial breeding industry is the province's important characteristics of aquaculture industry, forestry is one of the important industries of poverty alleviation. Due to the recent National People's Congress issued a new decision, but follow-up supporting policies have not yet followed, the wild animal breeding and Utilization Industry is facing the difficult situation of bankruptcy or debt.

On March 9,2020, Tu Xiaobin, director of the Wild Fauna and Flora Protection Bureau of the Jiangxi Provincial Forestry Bureau, told interface news that Jiangxi Province had not issued the above-mentioned documents, nor had they been submitted to the Ministry of Rural Agriculture and the State Forestry and grass administration. "It's all inside information. I don't know where it came from. "

On February 24th, the 13th Standing Committee of the National People's Congress voted and adopted the decision of the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress on comprehensively prohibiting illegal trade in wild animals, eradicating abusive practices of eating wild animals, and earnestly safeguarding the lives, health and safety of the People (hereinafter referred to as the decision) , making it clear that, starting from February 24, on the basis of the wild animals that were previously prohibited by law, the consumption of "land wild animals of important ecological, scientific and social value under state protection" as well as other land wild animals shall be completely prohibited, including artificial breeding, artificial breeding of wild land animals; a total ban for the purpose of food hunting, trading, transportation in the wild environment of natural growth and breeding of wild land animals.

On February 27, Liang Aifu, director of the Department of Supervision and administration of network transactions of the General Administration of market supervision, said at a press conference of the joint prevention and Control Mechanism of the State Council that according to the relevant laws on wildlife protection, previously, the focus has been on the protection of rare and endangered wildlife. "Now, according to the latest announcement by the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress, all wild land animals that are not listed in the catalogue of genetic resources of livestock and poultry will be banned from consumption. "

Prior to this, according to the Wildlife Protection Law (as amended in 2018) , the relevant policy, the scope of fasting is limited to the state's key protected wildlife, as the masked palm civets were not included, often "legal" to become some diners on the table "game. According to the latest decision, civets are not included in the list of genetic resources of livestock and poultry, and therefore may not be eaten.

Interface News noted that the above-mentioned "inventory of livestock and poultry genetic resources" originated from circular 2061 issued by the former Ministry of Agriculture in February 2014: In accordance with the provisions of Article 12 of the Animal Husbandry Law, and taking into account the results of the second national survey of livestock and poultry genetic resources, the list of National Livestock Genetic Resources Protection (Ministry of Agriculture of the People's Republic of China No. 662) has been revised, and 159 livestock and poultry breeds including Bamei pig have been identified as national livestock and poultry genetic resources protection breeds. The 159 breeds are divided into seven categories, namely pigs, chickens, ducks, geese, oxen, horses, Alpacas, sheep and other breeds.

According to the "request for instructions" in the above-mentioned online circular, if some wild animal and bird species with mature and stable artificial breeding techniques such as civets and bamboo rats are included in the "catalogue of livestock and Poultry Genetic Resources" , in accordance with the "Livestock Law" and other relevant laws and regulations, then the civets can enter the food range.

To this, Tu denied, "the power to stipulate fasting in the National People's Congress, the province does not have this power, we will strictly implement the relevant decisions of the NPC. "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
On May 23,2003, the Shenzhen Center for Disease Control and Prevention and the University of Hong Kong announced that the SARS virus found in wild civet cats was identical to that found in humans. Hong Kong has banned civet cats from entering the territory to prevent people from eating the meat that caused the SARS virus. Then, Guangdong, Shanghai and other places also banned the market civets trading.

In August 2003, the State Forestry Administration of the People's Republic of China published "a list of 54 species of wild land animals, including Sika deer, that are commercially available and have matured through the use of domesticated breeding techniques" . It is clear that its commercial operation and utilization of domestication breeding technology is mature, in accordance with China's relevant laws and regulations, may be engaged in commercial utilization of domestication breeding and management. In this regard, Guangxi, Hainan and other places also drafted a special "masked civet artificial breeding technical regulations. ".

The Jiangxi daily reported in November 2019 on the "get-rich experience" of raising civets in Wan'an County, Jiangxi Province: "30 female civets can produce about 90 civets, each of which can grow to 5 kg of commercial civets from half a year to a year. At 200 yuan per kg, 90 civets can be sold for 90,000 yuan. Excluding the cost, the annual profit is more than 50,000 yuan."In shaping, Gaopi and Baijia towns, there are 560 households with a total of more than 1,700 people supported by government departments, sign a contract to breed civets and head for the road to riches.

In an interview at that time, Tu Xiaobin said that after qualified quarantine and holding approval procedures (Forestry Department permission) , the artificially raised civet cat can circulate in the market and go to the dinner table, and the market prospects are very broad.

However, the sudden outbreak of new pneumonia, so that the public fully aware of the dangers of eating game, and reached a comprehensive "wild" consensus. Lu Zhi, a professor at the School of life sciences at Peking University, led a list of six species of wild animals that pose a threat to public safety, led by civet cats.

On February 27, the State Forestry and grassland administration announced a comprehensive reorganization of agencies engaged in the artificial breeding and management and utilization of wild animals, requiring those engaged in artificial breeding of wild animals for food purposes, the license or instrument issued for artificial breeding shall be withdrawn and cancelled, and the sale and transportation of wild animals for food shall be stopped without exception.

"Now we are mapping the wild animal breeding industry across the province in accordance with the unified national plan to find out what belongs to the catalogue of livestock and poultry genetic resources, what is used as medicine and what is used as food. The replacement of the replacement, the revocation of the revocation,"said Tu, there is a defined process for breeding wild animals, such as civet cats, which are used for both medicine and food, and some for fur processing. As to which can breed, relevant policy still waits for the country to make clear further.

According to industry insiders, the main purpose of raising civet cats in captivity is to serve as food, and total fasting means inevitable economic losses to the local community.

According to the request circulated on the Internet, there are 4,424 wild animal breeding units or individuals in Jiangxi Province, with fixed assets investment of 5.638 billion yuan and annual output value of 6.279 billion yuan, and 1,641 wild animal management and utilization units with an annual output value of 8.06 billion yuan, the industry employs more than 120,000 people. The province's wildlife artificial breeding industry involves 323 poverty alleviation projects, with a capital investment of 560 million yuan. The industry has helped 11,531 rural households find employment, involving 8,767 poor households that have set up file cards, of which 951 have yet to be lifted out of poverty, the wild animal breeding industry has increased the average income of poor households by more than 4,000 yuan or as much as 50,000 yuan, playing an important role in poverty alleviation.

The request stressed that due to the sudden introduction of the decision, the urgent adjustment of management policies, and the subsequent supporting policies that have not yet been followed up, it quickly caused extreme panic among those engaged in the artificial breeding and utilization of wild animals, in particular, some wildlife breeding enterprises and large households, involving a large number of loans, are facing the difficult situation of bankruptcy or heavy debts, directly affecting the vital interests of the grass-roots masses and social stability.

"The impact is really big. Jiangxi's wildlife breeding is mainly concentrated in the old areas, such as southern Jiangxi, which is related to local poverty alleviation. We are also waiting for the national policy, " said Tu Xiaobin, adding that in addition to the catalogue of livestock and Poultry Genetic Resources, if it involves food, the artificial breeding license must be revoked, involved in the pacification explanation, financial compensation should be put in place.

In this regard, the decision clearly states that the State Council and Local Government of the People's Republic of China shall take necessary measures to provide appropriate safeguards for the implementation of this decision. The relevant local Government of the People's Republic of China shall support, guide and assist affected farmers in adjusting and transforming their production and operation activities, and make certain compensation in accordance with the actual situation.

Referring to the catalogue of livestock and Poultry Genetic Resources, Liang Aifu, director of the Department of Supervision and administration of network transactions of the General Administration of market supervision, said at a State Council joint prevention and Control Mechanism press conference on February 27 that, "What will be in the catalogue in the future, still need next step to continuously perfect and perfect" .
